# {{ projectName }}

DARE-shaped Rust API on Axum 0.7. Layered Design (Handler → Service → Repository → Model).

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
docker compose up -d postgres
cargo install sqlx-cli --no-default-features --features postgres
sqlx database create
sqlx migrate run
cargo run
```

## Endpoints

- `POST /auth/login` — exchange email/password for JWT
- `GET /auth/me` — current user (Bearer JWT)
- `GET /users` — list users (paginated)
- `POST /users` — create user (admin only)
- `GET /ws` — WebSocket echo demo
- `GET /openapi.json` — OpenAPI 3.x surface
- `GET /swagger-ui` — Swagger UI

## Commands

- `cargo run` — dev server (port 8000)
- `cargo test --workspace` — tests
- `cargo clippy -- -D warnings` — lint
- `cargo audit` — dependency audit
- `sqlx migrate add <name>` — new migration
- `sqlx migrate run` — apply migrations

## DARE Method

See `.dare/skills.yml` for installed skills, `llms.txt` for agent context.
